---
import { BRAND_NAME } from "@/lib/config";
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-24 text-center">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">
    {BRAND_NAME} is preparing the next benchmark cycle
  </h1>
  <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
    No published cycle data is available yet. The leaderboard, humanizer
    pages, and comparison tools come back online once the next cycle
    publishes. Check the
    <a
      href="https://github.com/HumanizerBench/humanizerbench"
      class="underline underline-offset-4"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      target="_blank">public repository</a
    > for transparency artifacts as they land.
  </p>
</section>
